Bd4 Rb8 18. Nxf7 $1 Kxf7 19. g5 Bf5 (19... Nh5 $2 20. Rhg1 $16 {preventing ...
Ng3 and following up with strong attack after f4.}) 20. gxf6 Bxf6 21. Rhg1 Bxd4
22. Qxd4 g6 23. Rg2 Rb7 24. Qxd5+ Qxd5 25. Rxd5 Rbe7 26. Rd2 $14 {with a pawn
up in the endgame, though Black has some activity as compensation.}) 16... b5
17. Nh3 {liberating the path for the g5-push. Now the ideas with a sacrifice
