c4 14. Be2 Ne4 15. Qc1 d5 16. Bd4 Rac8 (16... Qb5 $5 17. Ka1 Rfe8) 17. Ne5 Nd6
$6 (17... Rfe8) (17... Bc5) 18. Bg4 {Black is already in trouble here} Rfe8 $2
